{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":false,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"CSSTranslate()","mdn_url":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSTranslate/CSSTranslate","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSTranslate\"><code>CSSTranslate</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Constructor</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><em><code>CSSTranslate()</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Properties</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSTranslate/x\"><code>x</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSTranslate/y\"><code>y</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSTranslate/z\"><code>z</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Inheritance:</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSTransformComponent\"><code>CSSTransformComponent</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"notecard experimental\" id=\"sect1\"><p><strong>Experimental:</strong> <strong>This is an <a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Writing_guidelines/Experimental_deprecated_obsolete#experimental\">experimental technology</a></strong><br>Check the <a href=\"#browser_compatibility\">Browser compatibility table</a> carefully before using this in production.</p></div>\n<p>\n  The <strong><code>CSSTranslate()</code></strong> constructor creates a\n  new <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSTranslate\"><code>CSSTranslate</code></a> object representing the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/transform-function/translate\">translate()</a> value of the\n  individual <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/transform\"><code>transform</code></a> property in CSS.\n</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js-nolint notranslate\">new CSSTranslate(x, y)\nnew CSSTranslate(x, y, z)\n</pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"x\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSTranslate/x\" title=\"x\"><code>x</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      A value for the x-axis of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSTranslate\"><code>CSSTranslate</code></a> object to be constructed.\n      This must be a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/length-percentage\"><code>&lt;length-percentage&gt;</code></a>.\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"y\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSTranslate/y\" title=\"y\"><code>y</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      A value for the y-axis of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSTranslate\"><code>CSSTranslate</code></a> object to be constructed.\n      This must be a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/length-percentage\"><code>&lt;length-percentage&gt;</code></a>.\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"z\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSTranslate/z\" title=\"z\"><code>z</code></a> <span class=\"badge inline optional\">Optional</span></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      A value for the z-axis of the <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSTranslate\"><code>CSSTranslate</code></a> object to be constructed.\n      This must be a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/length\"><code>&lt;length&gt;</code></a>.\n    </p>\n    <p>\n      If a value is passed for the <code>z-axis</code> this is a 3d transform. The value of\n      <code>is2D</code> will be set to false.\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"exceptions","title":"Exceptions","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n  <dt id=\"typeerror\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypeError\"><code>TypeError</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      Raised if the value of <code>CSSTranslate.x</code> or <code>CSSTranslate.y</code> is\n      not a <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/length-percentage\"><code>&lt;length-percentage&gt;</code></a>.\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n  <dt id=\"typeerror_2\"><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/TypeError\"><code>TypeError</code></a></dt>\n  <dd>\n    <p>\n      Raised if the value of <code>CSSTranslate.z</code> exists but is not a\n      <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/length\"><code>&lt;length&gt;</code></a>.\n    </p>\n  </dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"Examples","isH3":false,"content":"<p>To do</p>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"Specifications","id":"specifications","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://drafts.css-houdini.org/css-typed-om/#dom-csstranslate-csstranslate","title":"CSS Typed OM Level 2"}],"query":"api.CSSTranslate.CSSTranslate"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.CSSTranslate.CSSTranslate","dataURL":"/en-US/docs/Web/API/CSSTranslate/CSSTranslate/bcd.json"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Examples","id":"examples"},{"text":"Specifications","id":"specifications"},{"text":"Browser compatibility","id":"browser_compatibility"}],"summary":"The CSSTranslate() constructor creates a\n  new CSSTranslate object representing the translate() value of the\n  individual transform property in CSS.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-09-13T05:21:27.000Z","source":{"folder":"en-us/web/api/csstranslate/csstranslate","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/api/csstranslate/csstranslate/index.md","last_commit_u